Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.85,0:00:03.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龐大的力量蘊於其身
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.54,0:00:06.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有烙印了宿命的人才有權享受
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.30,0:00:08.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無盡的快感
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.30,0:00:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 毀滅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.31,0:00:11.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Witch Blade
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.84,0:00:14.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在 一名女性覺醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.03,0:01:55.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志織
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.81,0:02:00.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.02,0:02:04.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把Blade收回去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.19,0:02:08.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.46,0:02:12.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 這…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.18,0:02:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.92,0:02:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.75,0:02:19.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不相信會發生這樣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.62,0:02:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鎮定下來  志織
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.63,0:02:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的身體只是發生了一點變化
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.03,0:02:25.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變化?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.34,0:02:28.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的 我會看護你的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.31,0:02:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師 你給我…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.54,0:02:37.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你明白 老師
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.35,0:02:40.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有那種意思
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.94,0:02:46.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是覺得感覺很好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.48,0:02:50.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 是那樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.29,0:02:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就… 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.98,0:02:57.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後再說 慢慢的說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.64,0:03:01.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺…實在是太…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.92,0:03:15.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志織
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.56,0:03:22.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在找這艘遊艇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.17,0:03:25.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知不知道呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.01,0:03:32.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一等  打擾一下可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.77,0:03:34.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這艘遊艇…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.61,0:03:42.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在海上倒是見過這樣的船
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.49,0:03:49.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可忘了在哪見過了 還有在哪停泊什麼的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.43,0:03:51.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任何事情都行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.57,0:03:56.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種級別的船 像是遠航用的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.44,0:03:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停泊港不一定是東京
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.40,0:04:01.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許是橫濱 千葉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.15,0:04:03.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可能是更遠的地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.18,0:04:06.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找起來是不是太困難了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.28,0:04:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.49,0:04:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.69,0:04:19.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己去找實在是太難了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.06,0:04:30.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.31,0:04:37.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼一回事 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.53,0:04:39.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前怎麼說是敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.02,0:04:43.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們倆在騙我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.38,0:04:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那兩個人是Lady和你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.35,0:04:51.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好給我解釋清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.73,0:04:55.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然的話 是無法安心工作的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.09,0:04:58.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.71,0:05:02.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還記得我說過
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.38,0:05:05.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我們導示和NswF共同研究WitchBlade」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.38,0:05:07.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.67,0:05:08.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.88,0:05:12.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時NswF向我們這派遣過一名女性
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.68,0:05:14.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是Lady
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.69,0:05:23.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是NswF派遣來共同研究WitchBlade的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.03,0:05:25.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫穌峰玲奈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.15,0:05:28.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是鷹山 請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.18,0:05:32.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個很優秀的女性
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.87,0:05:38.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知性道德 體力相貌 全部都…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.60,0:05:44.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NswF培養成的NEO-GIN是這樣的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.74,0:05:45.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很讓人震驚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.16,0:05:51.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.87,0:05:56.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒價值的故事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.92,0:06:00.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用那種說法也可以嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.96,0:06:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還認為你是不會戀愛的木頭人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.30,0:06:07.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起戀愛的話 就有些微妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.74,0:06:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.73,0:06:15.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有任何前兆就在我的面前突然消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.81,0:06:17.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失了?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.81,0:06:20.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在研究進入緊要關頭時
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.56,0:06:23.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲奈偷了WitchBlade逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.80,0:06:28.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,WitchBlade被盜走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.48,0:06:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是穌峰老師她…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.85,0:06:36.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最初以為那是NswF的指示而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.72,0:06:41.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲奈和WitchBlade一起 完全沒了蹤影
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.36,0:06:43.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.31,0:06:46.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許本來就是有這個想法了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.40,0:06:49.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想把WitchBlade據為己有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.00,0:06:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確WitchBlade是會選擇適合自己的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.93,0:06:58.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 玲奈是WitchBlade的有力人選
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.32,0:07:01.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.49,0:07:04.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在研究中知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.58,0:07:08.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不可能裝備給NswF的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.34,0:07:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有傳聞說 要把玲奈從研究員裡調出來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.68,0:07:20.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在那之前 她和WitchBlade都消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.23,0:07:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背叛了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.64,0:07:29.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有那種想法 很難說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.01,0:07:31.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這種關係呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.17,0:07:34.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NEO-GIN可是教父的掌上明珠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.33,0:07:39.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲奈只是對初次認識的男女關係有興趣罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.77,0:07:42.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你怎麼想的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.22,0:07:47.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陳舊的往事了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.30,0:07:52.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大腦的舊皮質
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.30,0:07:52.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}舊皮質<archipallium>\h腦外皮層的部分\h位於前腦即覆蓋在側腦室之上的腦組織\N主要掌管著\h人的性格 慾望 情緒等等的感性思維
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.83,0:07:55.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特別是對邊緣的刺激的增加
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.52,0:07:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼它會和Blade的行動同步呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.08,0:08:01.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為它會刺激裝備者的本能
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.11,0:08:04.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,導致更加渴望戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.39,0:08:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是對人的束縛…還是說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.06,0:08:16.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊 這個樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.97,0:08:21.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜梅啊 沒有什麼可害羞的 這樣很萌哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.97,0:08:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜梅 真的很可愛呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.39,0:08:30.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話 會招來厄運的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.20,0:08:36.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子很怕生的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.84,0:08:39.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顯眼的裝扮是起反效果的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.71,0:08:42.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姐頭就不要嘲笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.52,0:08:43.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.88,0:08:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 找到了 找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.44,0:08:46.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.38,0:08:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這回是什麼事 想借錢的話 我可沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.58,0:08:51.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.77,0:08:55.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話… 大姐姐她們…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.36,0:08:58.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.47,0:09:01.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事早說呀 斗澤
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.72,0:09:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 長先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.23,0:09:04.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.15,0:09:11.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了來了來了 這種事情當然不能放著不管
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.16,0:09:13.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.70,0:09:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺到了 走上了歪路
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.19,0:09:23.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣子的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.89,0:09:24.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 小子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.90,0:09:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我照片 這邊這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.60,0:09:33.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你想查什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.39,0:09:37.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船主或者停泊港之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.98,0:09:38.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.15,0:09:41.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 斗澤
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.93,0:09:44.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的會幫我準備聯誼會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.13,0:09:47.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會錯的 當然 絕對的事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.83,0:09:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說話算數哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.12,0:09:53.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯誼會?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.47,0:10:00.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 那麼就和世界上的OTAKU打個招呼試試吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.80,0:10:02.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 CheckCheck TwoOneTwo
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.63,0:10:04.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hello
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.27,0:10:05.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hi Chuyo SAMA What's up
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.79,0:10:07.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nobady want to help me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.76,0:10:11.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 好厲害呀 長先生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.96,0:10:14.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,こよい お宅…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.83,0:10:24.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 在崩潰著 志織的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.82,0:10:32.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的志織和X-CON是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.42,0:10:35.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在追求著更強的快感
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.97,0:10:37.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.41,0:10:39.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續下去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.71,0:10:48.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於這件事 我認為有必要繼續進行調查
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.34,0:10:51.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為現狀 為了找到進一步的資料 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.13,0:10:54.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確保志織是緊急事件
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.45,0:10:55.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.22,0:11:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想找個人來和我戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.55,0:11:36.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.14,0:11:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會讓我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.45,0:11:57.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咖啡奶酒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.66,0:12:00.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我唯一會做的雞尾酒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.92,0:12:07.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好甜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.30,0:12:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能不適合你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.77,0:12:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.62,0:12:14.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.68,0:12:17.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡有個位置空著
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.78,0:12:21.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得不太好 缺了一個之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.18,0:12:28.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 WitchBlade不是被Lady偷走了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.51,0:12:31.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼現在會在我的身上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.29,0:12:34.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原因我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.29,0:12:39.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 在大地震的時候裝配到你身上的 是沒錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.45,0:12:44.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一天 知道了玲奈的位置的我們
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.75,0:12:48.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在WitchBlade的回收中 投入了I-Weapon
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.41,0:12:53.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可與此同時 NswF送來了姊妹們
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.89,0:12:56.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和預想一樣沒能避免衝突
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.70,0:13:01.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼此過分追究的結果 招致了最壞的事態
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.50,0:13:16.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉睡中的WitchBlade覺醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.11,0:13:20.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這之後 發生了那場大地震
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.97,0:13:26.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時正好在那啊 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.94,0:13:28.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這麼一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.14,0:13:32.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命中注定嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.60,0:13:38.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 為什麼玲奈沒有裝配上WitchBlade
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.50,0:13:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.36,0:13:39.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.43,0:13:45.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎樣 玲奈回到NswF裝備了ClonBlade
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.83,0:13:49.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教父沒有生玲奈的氣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.57,0:13:52.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得的與WitchBlade適合的人 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.93,0:13:56.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不會輕易放手的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.63,0:13:58.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然為了這種東西…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.70,0:14:02.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強大的力量是很吸引人的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.92,0:14:04.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是男人們的邏輯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.01,0:14:08.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定理解不了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.33,0:14:13.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用這個東西的可怕之處…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.17,0:14:28.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,局長 還有大約30分鐘就靠岸了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.49,0:14:28.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.37,0:14:31.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.92,0:14:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是…很長啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.76,0:14:43.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厲害啊 長先生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.38,0:14:45.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十分鐘就找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.87,0:14:50.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿西娜停泊港啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.26,0:14:55.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 只要知道了那個遊艇的主人的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.42,0:14:56.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.05,0:14:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 怎麼回事 你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.85,0:15:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斗澤君在打我媽媽的主意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.80,0:15:05.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斗澤君? 誰也沒打正·胸小姐的主意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.90,0:15:07.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來監視你說的是不是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.14,0:15:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 快下去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.43,0:15:11.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 絕對不下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.25,0:15:17.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 我這可是很趕時間的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.25,0:15:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 媽媽喜歡的類型並不是斗澤這樣的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.14,0:15:23.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 你完全理解錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.78,0:15:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走吧 媽媽那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.46,0:15:28.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 我不管那麼多了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.47,0:15:34.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在附近
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.56,0:15:38.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這種感覺…和以前不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.04,0:15:40.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不快些的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.84,0:15:53.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 那個女人在哪 快交出來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.96,0:15:56.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在說我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.74,0:16:00.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.84,0:16:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 我還沒滿足
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.24,0:16:07.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.81,0:16:13.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,局長 不好了 雅音還沒有完全恢復呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.52,0:16:15.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去掩護她
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.47,0:16:15.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.93,0:16:22.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個呀 這個
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.27,0:16:59.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鷹山澪士 老師的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.03,0:17:08.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的對手 是這邊哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.73,0:17:18.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對你已經沒任何感覺了 辜負了我的期望
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.94,0:17:36.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,局長
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.50,0:17:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別想逃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.08,0:17:50.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.58,0:18:23.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.21,0:18:25.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.15,0:18:38.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志織…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.96,0:18:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的秘書好像到這裡來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.71,0:18:43.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.28,0:18:47.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,局長 要怎麼處理ClonBlade
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.75,0:18:49.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志織的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.71,0:18:52.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.94,0:18:56.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要檢驗屍體
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.01,0:18:57.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有屍體
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.30,0:18:59.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.21,0:19:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這個哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.47,0:19:04.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結晶化成了這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.43,0:19:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 能給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.26,0:19:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿著回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.05,0:19:14.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除此之外 沒有任何可以給你的了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.31,0:19:16.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志織是我的秘書呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.07,0:19:17.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.81,0:19:25.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.30,0:19:28.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽  
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.01,0:19:33.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨穗子 你怎麼會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.82,0:19:34.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚇一跳了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.26,0:19:37.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和斗澤一起來的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.89,0:19:39.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斗澤?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.79,0:19:43.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.97,0:19:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.57,0:19:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是船的主人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.48,0:19:49.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我介紹一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.61,0:19:56.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到了發生在高架橋下的那件事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.12,0:20:04.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了 但今天就先這樣以後再解釋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.65,0:20:06.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 只能這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.62,0:20:08.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.75,0:20:11.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.66,0:20:15.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澪士
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.89,0:20:18.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志織的死是因為ClonBlade哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.21,0:20:19.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.65,0:20:24.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早晚我可能也會變成那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.31,0:20:28.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是WitchBlade也是一樣的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.29,0:20:33.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎樣ClonBlade是仿照WitchBlade做的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.64,0:20:39.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前一起查閱的老資料上記載的事 還記得嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.26,0:20:45.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然WitchBlade有強大力量 但可能會傷害裝備者
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.91,0:20:48.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時沒能去確認啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.50,0:20:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在確認了 WitchBlade會傷害裝備者的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.52,0:21:03.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且WitchBlade一旦取下來 就是裝備者死的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.15,0:21:10.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪個先壞掉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.24,0:21:14.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何 暫且老實一點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.75,0:23:13.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～～ 如梨穗子所說
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.81,0:23:16.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斗澤好像在打媽媽的主意
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.85,0:23:19.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 雖然不是那個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.12,0:23:25.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎樣 把不想讓人知道的事拍成照片來賺錢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.12,0:23:25.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實在是太差勁了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.44,0:23:28.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不會和這類人做朋友的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.39,0:23:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但據瑪麗子所說
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.96,0:23:34.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前斗澤曾經拍過很好的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.17,0:23:35.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.50,0:23:38.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點讓人難以相信啊
